{"tid":2344884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中國公民記者張展採訪武漢疫情判監 4 年】","createTime":"2020-12-29T05:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T05:56:25.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9a531648cf3c1e2506f7001470422f0607c8cdf7","tid":2344884,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T05:56:25.000Z","msg":"【中國公民記者張展採訪武漢疫情判監 4 年】<br />\n<br />\n中國公民記者張展，今年 2 月到武漢採訪疫情，回上海後被捕，昨日尋釁滋事罪成判監 4 年，她的母親接受有線中國組訪問，稱要對女兒說對不起，因為自小教導她做人要誠實講真話，結果女兒因而受罪。<br />\n<br />\n相關報道：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3pAS48J\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3pAS48J&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=b56b0d9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3pAS48J</a><br />\n<br />\n有線中國組link<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fb.watch/2GvCMsdd-g/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.watch%2F2GvCMsdd-g%2F&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=10734c12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fb.watch/2GvCMsdd-g/</a>"}]}